ablished 2023</span><h1 class=\"text-7xl md:text-[12rem] font-black text-white tracking-tighter mb-8 italic leading-none drop-shadow-2xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\">Vault 6 Studios<span class=\"text-blue-600 animate-pulse\">.</span></h1><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><button class=\"group relative bg-white text-black px-12 py-6 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] flex items-center gap-4 hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white transition-all overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500 ease-out z-0\"></div><span class=\"relative z-10\">Enter Vault</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right relative z-10 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button><a href=\"/shop\" class=\"text-[9px] md:text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors border-b border-transparent hover:border-white pb-1\">Browse the Archive</a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-5 border-b border-gray-900 bg-[#020202] overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap relative\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#020202] to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-24 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#020202] to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center animate-marquee\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-12 min-w-max px-12\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-500\">SYNDICATE</span><span class=\"text-[10